Advantages of maven?

            3.1. Project Management tool. (auto generate the file/folder structure).                
                    
            3.2. Automated Build tool. - lifecycle phases
            
            3.3. Managing repositories.
            
                    4.3.1. Local repo.
                    4.3.2. Central repo.
                    4.3.3. Remote repo.
                    
